#25 officially started. As expected, there's a few things I needed to change 
on the layout, that's what the proto type boards are for. The blue jumper 
wires are #30 wire-wrap wire. I could get rid of the jumpers by going to 4 
layer boards, but that more than doubles the cost. This is both the linear 
and random sweep sections shown here.

Frank-S
